## ğŸ’¡ Usage

```bash
# Quick Start
jarvis

# Using Specific Model
jarvis --platform ollama --model qwen2.5:14b

# Custom Ollama API
jarvis --platform ollama --model llama3.2 --api-base http://localhost:11434
```

